law.history: Repealed 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 66, sec. 20, effective March 16, 1994. -- Created 1992 Ky. Acts ch. 461, sec. 3, effective April 13, 1992.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Effect of failure to comply with KRS 528.010, 528.130, and 528.140 -- Fraud in registration -- Suspension or revocation of registration.
